description:
The purpose of the thesis was to investigate, assess, and establish the material&nbsp; 
management practices, problems, and solutions on the building construction&nbsp; 
sites in Somalia. Mixed research method was used because it combines&nbsp; 
quantitative and qualitative research methods, procedures, approaches, ideas, or&nbsp; 
language into a single study. The sample size for this study was determined to&nbsp; 
be 100. The questionnaire was used for this research study to ensure simplicity&nbsp; 
and accuracy.

